Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}着急{\c&H000000&}更占多数
