Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人は生まれながら光と影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:43.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光と影を纏い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Their only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:54.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}欲しいもの全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:59.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手に入れること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:06.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}それが幸せなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:11.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}誰かが笑顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:17.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どこかできっと泣いてる人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:28.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}すれ違うほど　愛おしく思う気持ちがある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:33.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ひとときのあいだに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:40.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕らはみんな矛盾を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:48.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あしたへの光を見つめながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:52.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}歩いてくのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人类从出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:43.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就一直缠绕着光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:54.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将一切想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:59.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}都收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:06.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那真的就幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:11.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果有人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:17.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那一定在某处也有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:28.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}每当擦肩而过 就会觉得怜爱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:33.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在转瞬而逝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:40.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们都会怀抱着矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:48.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够一直看着通向明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:52.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一直走下去吗
