Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有缠创者听令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要死守这个次元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要从奈兹的猛攻下守住我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在时机到来前一定要坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹 正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您将「门」关上了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于正式成为了退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很快期未考试就到了 把我急得焦头烂额
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过多亏露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我顺利挺过了考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并迎来了期待已久的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 是大海 能看到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看到大海会不会情不自禁地想大喊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻真是积极乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 别人经常这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 缠就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 栞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一个失职的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那个体力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是休假 就让我好好休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次旅行是你计划的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要选这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能开车过来 并且预算能控制最低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么去我们天万神社的姐妹神社 天海神社怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就在海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有修行者用的住宿设施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅提供用餐 还有温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我打声招呼 几乎可以免费入住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必介绍给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐意至极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就选了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选这里的原因真的只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得你是个务实的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做没有利益的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想为别人做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么你把波奇也叫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手塚？我没邀请他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是你邀请的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能邀请他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 他为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说这两周没有发生任何事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她们也太悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克 你果然来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真见外 我们不是共同抵御恶灵的战友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要站在这了 和我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道小克你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经帮你准备好泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 小克也和我们一起住神社过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 小克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用那种奇怪的方式介绍我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…贫富差距社会？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手塚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发美女和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是后宫状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那个后宫的中心并没有手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他居然这么蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克 来一起玩个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都来海边了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要玩个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看行李的任务就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和露谢拉小姐二人世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}我没带 跳不我跳几下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 真的抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IATO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这附近的天海神社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海神社是皇缠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看 该不该告诉小缠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 所以你才选择了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你为什么要告诉我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得将情报共享比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为将缠她们带到这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会发生些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是IATO的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把冰快打碎 早浇上糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能让普通的水变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Cool Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷日本政策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是天海神社？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海神社是供奉海神的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 几位是天万神社的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天海神社的雨音弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不巧 神社的宫司不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以将由我来接待大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该我们请您关照才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是手塚秀夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是弥生 雨音弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弥生啊 你长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说都已经成大姑娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我第一次见您的时候 我还是初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是皇先生的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我叫皇缠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛和栞大人一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我还是见习巫女时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲是我的前辈 给了我很多帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈曾经是巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经在这里生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是人间天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐很美味 温泉也是相当棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淋浴在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把妈妈曾经在这里当过巫女的事告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怕我想起妈妈 所以才没说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还正在犹豫要不要说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想被抓吗 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊 伸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在尽警官的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲自验证能否偷窥以确保他们的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这面墙十分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕你能这么无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的温泉还满意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经在房间里好被子了 请好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以问件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈当时在神社里 过着怎样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在我和你差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这座天海神社当见习巫女时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲作为神社的巫女 工作十分出色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她十分活泼开朗 从不区别待人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是我理想中的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然相处时间不长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从你母亲哪里学到了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女的礼仪 心态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及做人该有的生活态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以现在能在这座神社当巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为有你母亲的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妈妈真出色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 非常出色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和伸吾君是什么时候遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时她在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是直接问你父亲比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那应该是他们两人宝贵回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 试胆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上这座神社附近的岩地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个有名的灵异地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 小克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫上手塚先生 你爸爸和露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs62}别去了 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}试胆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很怕那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}试胆啊 试胆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 试胆是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 由麻主办的试胆大会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一组 按签上的顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边的岩地转上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边还有吊桥 刺激感绝佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露谢拉老师 C组
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克是B组
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个可以让我来抽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发美女的C
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者金发美少女的B
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C或B C或B
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想要这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话该我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经看不到小缠爸爸他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一组是小缠和小克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明和奈兹战斗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和那是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 很热的 离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行也得行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样走路很不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个反应很好 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次试胆大会没有白组织
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻真是喜欢搞活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的座右铭就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底享受人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你执行得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很有气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅让人烦躁还很热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心理却觉得我这个部下很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分啊 伸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和清水还有葛西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波奇 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心快崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你还有功夫开玩笑那就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去通知缠她们避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚有没有听到类似惨叫的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有人在跟我们做一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然能这么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我就是被这么训练出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒奈兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 我是伸吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸 伸吾君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回神社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也叫后面来的由麻她们一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为好奇跑来现场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我可是刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 雕具座的门开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为好奇跑来现场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 你不用去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统关闭 限制已解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维度变换 等级3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白 我一定会保护你亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 由麻 还有露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DR反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹竟然有这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 既然有恶灵我们必须将其消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君让我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为好奇去现场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护小缠 完成约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一名刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是一名父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让伸吾君为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已经是一名退魔少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吸收攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻击没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少将它带到高次元去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就用最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神罚天雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被恶灵吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用一击就将那个奈兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 只是晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是皇先生有个万一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没脸见栞大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君所讲述的他对妈妈的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他对我的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些情感与我的愿望是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠将成为缠创巫女
